text: I like the dreams of the future better than the history of the past.
Lost time is never found again.
Friendship needs no words - it is solitude delivered from the anguish of loneliness.
Give someone a second chance. Not because they deserve it; but cos you might be the one who change his/her life.
If you love something let it go. If it comes back to you; it is yours. If it doesn't; it never was
